column3: “So for some reason at my dispensary (well in all of Ct) they can't use street strain names
column5: or OG kush. So they call this #25
column6: violet-but in reality it's tres dawg. Anyways great strain
column7: especially if you're an indica lover(like me.) it's actually a hybrid but definitely an indica dominant one.  A little goes a long way with this strain. Relaxing
column8: helps with pain(I shattered my ankle in a really ba...”"

column3: “This is a great indica for all your relaxation needs. Smells so nice, excellent fragrance. Very strong effects come on quick. I would probably not use this strain during the day. Get this if you can find it and you love good strong bud.”

“So first of all I was reading over the effects here and it says uplifting & energetic. I would have to go ahead & say no that isn't the case. It's definitely a strong leaning indica hybrid.
Form: Shatter
Brand: HYH Society
THC: 74%

Trees dawg is worth a try & I guess it's sort of rare?

Smell 5/5
 It smells like my grandma's house. Or my friends basement. A definite maybe moldy smell but not in a bad way? I like the...”
“Parents Chem Dawg (not Star Dawg, as I inaccurately previously posted)”
“Great strain, I'd give it a 4.5 but I can't so a 5. At my dispensary they call it violet/25 since in Ct our dispensarys can't use street names." Ridiculous
column4: since the pharmacist tells me anyway. Great indica
column5: if you can get your hands on it
column6: I suggest you do. Super high thc content(mine tested at 25.3%) long lasting
column7: relaxing high. Definitely in my top 10.”"

column3:
“This is a SUPER potent strain! It's sticky, it smells pungent - but it's a goooood pungent :) One small bowl and i'm soaring. This review has taken about 10 minutes to type up... 

If you already have some kind of nervousness or paranoia, this strain will amplify it.

The highness feels like its radiating from my eyes and chest. I'm very tingly. Like a post orgasm”
“Slow to come on effects, leaving a highly clear state of euphoria that makes this a good of afternoon strain or weekend wake and bake”
“This is a back-cross of my absolute favorite cannabis strain: Chemdawg. Very potent, not for the casual smoker.”

“Very sweet sour diesel chemdawg taste. Less hashy than headband. Really flavorful. Offers a medium sativa high with heavy indica stone. One of the best mixes of diesel flavor. This strain is very strong and the oil is amazing. If you are lucky enough to find this strain get it.”
“Nice relaxing and europhic high from this!”
“This is a back-cross of my absolute favorite cannabis strain: Chemdawg. Very potent, not for the casual smoker.”

“I tried this one tonight. I was thinking it was gonna be a good bedtime one but Nope!!!! This strain is gonna be my new party time one. Very euphoric was listening to music and I rocked that garage lol.”
“Indicated knock out”
“This is great for pain and stress!”
“Damn good stuff, potent indica with good funky smell and taste...”
“ducky stain ever teas like boooo”
“Near perfect cut sitting in front of me. I love this strain 9.4/10”

“Good weed, nice relaxing body and head high and cures loss of appetite easily. Can definitely feel the Indica effects quite a bit too through sleepiness. High THC content so not much needed to get you blasted.”

“4.5 CT Strain Violet by Curaleaf. This one was so smooth, more of Indica then hybrid I would say with a very quick onset of body tingling and then face got numb very quick and on hour 2 still feeling great. Making me sleepy as well which is what I want. Would not be productive on this guy.”

“I've only tried the Shatter and wow this strain will put any veteran smoker to sleep. Also works great with pain. Only down side is if you smoke to much and fight the sleep you can easily get paranoid.”
“Daily smoker for 35 years. love this strain. It's a zombie couch lock high. High comes on quick and has good flavor.”

“The packaging on this Tres Dawg has a pug on it and labeled a hybrid. Organtica is a new dispensary just opened on the 28th of October of 2016. I am really excited for this dispensary because of the different strains they are having from strains I've never seen nor heard like Polar Ice Cap" is one and they also have DJ Shorts Actual blueberry from DJ short himself. This place really has got to be my new favorite pla...”"
“Really enjoyed this.”
“Wow...Exceptional very pungent with a smooth vapor. Definitely a night time weed. Good to Netflix and chill.”
“Solid bud,,,,  knock out buzz ,,stoney”
“Kick ass hybrid, from MMJTHC, look, smell, taste, to effect, all winners. A morning to mid afternoon strain, get/keep busy strain.”
“Very powerful strain. I've been smoking shatter for 8 years and 2 dabs of Tres Dawg I was ready to pass out. Also good for pain.”
“so if your female this is the one when your monthly friend comes stock up on this one...”
